{"tid":2328334,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌哂你地老母成個連登都係李偲嫣嘅post","createTime":"2020-12-16T13:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T14:20:38.000Z","uid":15886,"like":11,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6b68d848c21271256d1d092d07762bea908e81","tid":2328334,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？ <br />\n做咩成個熱門都係李偲嫣post？<br />\n如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死 <br />\n連我個淺藍老母都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 外國戰線著哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應承我 唔可以當手足係condom？<br />\n我哋揸住佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 千祈唔可以中五毛分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸"},{"pid":"f2b9caf0342a6b0feefaf5b6b3a843191c3d14ee","tid":2328334,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f85b9a9c35ed2696b555db85a30310473f03729","tid":2328334,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"點睇#2"},{"pid":"09fba1054f662edaa07a541270bc28d36ccb1d6d","tid":2328334,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f85b9a9c35ed2696b555db85a30310473f03729","tid":2328334,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"點睇#2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"起咗底  偽黃五毛"},{"pid":"f89c74c27ab5d37931c0304bd53cf19c564e36a3","tid":2328334,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09fba1054f662edaa07a541270bc28d36ccb1d6d","tid":2328334,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f85b9a9c35ed2696b555db85a30310473f03729","tid":2328334,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"點睇#2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T1